Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.59,0:44:30.93,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢を叶えて
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.20,0:44:37.75,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}一人で探してた星の
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.25,0:44:42.17,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}同じ光を
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.46,0:44:48.53,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が見つめているだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.03,0:44:55.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつもの夜が闇に染まる頃
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.55,0:45:00.02,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}走り出せるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.15,0:45:14.21,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,1000)\blur3}一人じゃない心たちのように
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------INCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.59,0:44:30.93,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}实现梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.20,0:44:37.75,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}一个人探索着行星的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.25,0:44:42.17,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}在同样的光芒下
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.46,0:44:48.53,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}我的眼中只注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.03,0:44:55.91,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}在寻常的夜晚被黑暗染上之时
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.55,0:45:00.02,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,100)\blur3}就应该奔跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.15,0:45:14.21,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(100,1000)\blur3}就像并非独自一人的心灵一样
